  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Brighter Day Enrichment Academy (BDEA) is located in Ward 8 of Washington, DC, the city&apos;s poorest neighborhood. We strive to break the cycle of poverty by providing elementary school students with academic enrichment such as literacy instruction, homework assistance and STEM.  We also offer cultural enrichment opportunities to expand our students&apos; understanding of their place in the world.  These opportunities include instruction in the languages, history and culture of our global neighbors.</narrative>
  </description>
